enb_long_title: 42nd Session of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change (IPCC-42)
sentences: This session (26-29 October 2009, Bali, Indonesia) approved the proposed AR5 chapter outlines.

The Panel also considered progress on implementing decisions taken at IPCC-30 regarding the involvement of scientists from developing countries and countries with economies in transition, use of electronic technologies, and the longer-term future of the IPCC.
